223
00:13:09,125 --> 00:13:11,500
- YEAH. THIS MUST BE HARD.

224
00:13:11,583 --> 00:13:15,250
- IT IS.
I REMEMBER SO MUCH.

225
00:13:15,333 --> 00:13:18,083
- SO, WHAT DO YOU KNOW
ABOUT THESE PAINTINGS OVER HERE?

226
00:13:20,041 --> 00:13:22,375
- I DON'T THINK I'VE EVER
