HER IMAGE TO TRICK ME!

235
00:14:01,541 --> 00:14:04,375
- COME ON KINKEL! STOP BEING
A COWARD AND SHOW YOURSELF!

236
00:14:05,958 --> 00:14:07,125
- ( chuckles )

237
00:14:07,208 --> 00:14:10,458
- COME ON!
I'M NOT PLAYING AROUND!

238
00:14:10,541 --> 00:14:14,666
- AM I TO UNDERSTAND THAT YOU'RE
THREATENING ME, KOUHEI MORIOKA?

239
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:16,541
- MAYBE!

240
00:14:16,625 --> 00:14:17,791
- REALLY, MISTRESS LUNA,

241
00:14:17,875 --> 00:14:20,333
