CAN ONLY BRING RUIN TO OUR KIND.

243
00:14:28,208 --> 00:14:32,375
HIS POISONED BLOOD ROBS YOU OF
THE VERY ESSENCE OF WHO YOU ARE.

244
00:14:33,166 --> 00:14:34,208
IT NUMBS YOU.

245
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:41,750
