OF OUR DIVINE SLUMBER.

251
00:15:00,583 --> 00:15:04,625
PLEASE, AWAKEN FROM THIS
NIGHTMARE AND COME HOME TO ME.

252
00:15:04,708 --> 00:15:07,916
- YOU'RE THE NIGHTMARE,
NOT KOUHEI.

253
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,833
PREPARE YOURSELF,

254
00:15:09,916 --> 00:15:12,916
