288
00:17:24,625 --> 00:17:26,208
- WHAT? I DON'T
EVEN UNDERSTAND

289
00:17:26,291 --> 00:17:27,916
WHAT GAMES YOU'RE
PLAYING ANYMORE.

290
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:30,791
BUT HEY, IF YOU REALLY
WANT A CHALLENGE,

291
00:17:30,875 --> 00:17:32,541
THEN HOW'S THIS FOR A GAME?

292
00:17:33,958 --> 00:17:35,166
- GOYO HAKKE!

293
00:17:48,250 --> 00:17:49,291
- KOUHEI!

294
00:17:50,875 --> 00:17:52,458
- ( screaming ) NO!

295
00:17:54,625 --> 00:17:58,500
HAZUKI! NO, PLEASE! JUST LET
GO OF ME AND GET OUT OF HERE!

296
00:17:58,583 --> 00:18:02,708
- WOULD YOU STOP TELLING ME
WHAT TO DO? AND GO ON A DIET!

297
00:18:02,791 --> 00:18:05,958
- WAIT, IS IT REALLY YOU?
YOU SEEM GENUINE.

298
00:18:06,041 --> 00:18:08,416
TELL ME, ARE YOU THE REAL
KOUHEI AND THE REAL HAZUKI?

299
00:18:08,500 --> 00:18:11,375
- WELL, OF COURSE IT'S US!
- WHO ELSE WOULD WE BE?

300
00:18:11,458 --> 00:18:15,208
- I SEE. NO WONDER MY SPELLS
WOULDN'T WORK ON YOU.

301
00:18:15,291 --> 00:18:19,333
- OH, NO WAY. YOU GET AWAY
