338
00:19:57,666 --> 00:20:00,583
NOW, PREPARE YOURSELF!

339
00:20:10,458 --> 00:20:12,208
KINKEL!

340
00:20:15,291 --> 00:20:18,125
- THIS CAN'T BE HER POWER!

341
00:20:20,625 --> 00:20:25,000
DAMN YOU. VAMPIRE'S LOVER!

342
00:20:28,625 --> 00:20:29,833
- ( sighs )

343
00:20:29,916 --> 00:20:30,958
- YOU OKAY?

344
00:20:32,375 --> 00:20:33,750
